ComicInfo.Title: Snake Hunt Part 1
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Snake Hunt Part 1: Cobra Commander gets a drone inside of Fort Wadsworth's motor pool while Snake Eyes is sparring against four of the Joes, but Snake Eyes destroys the drone. However, there is a team of Cobra vipers hidden in a residential home just outside of Fort Wadsworth.
